                <h1 class="domdom">03</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1420">The Stuart Hall Project (2013)</a></h1>

                <h2>3 Sep 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>John
Akomfrah's sensitive and emotionally charged portrait of cultural theorist
Stuart Hall (1932 - 2014).</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1420">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

            </section>
