                <h1 class="domdom">11</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1421">Kenny</a></h1>

                <h2>11 Sep 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>"None are less visible than those we decide not to see"- Kenny, Part
philosopher, part comedian, juggles family tensions, fatherhood
and sewage with charm, humour and unflinching dignity. </p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1421">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

            </section>
