                <h1 class="domdom">08</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1423">Dr. Strangelove, Or: How I Learned To Stop Worrying And Love The Bomb</a></h1>

                <h2>8 Oct 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>“Gentlemen, you can’t fight in here! This is the War Room.” 50 years since it's release - Kubrick's classic cold-war satire in which the top brass of the American and Russian governments must decide if they want to begin a nuclear war. Nominated for several major Academy Awards, including Best Picture! </p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1423">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

